{"tid":1158180,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"墨子說：國之將亡，必有七患","createTime":"2019-05-16T19:31:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T18:46:39.000Z","uid":247311,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"99d365619d233f85a0b6658cde226697eb9c278c","tid":1158180,"uid":247311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T19:31:47.000Z","msg":"墨子說：國之將亡，必有七患<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 國防之患：不修國防  大興宮殿  粉飾太平(一帶一路，大灣區好勁）<br />\n2. 外交之患：大敵當前  外無盟友  孤立無援（大小諸國皆圍攻之)<br />\n3. 財政之患：分配不公  鋪張浪費  窮盡民用（大白象，低端人口）<br />\n4. 內政之患：仕皆漁私  修法禁言  不問國是（商界要死頂唔係俾人打靶）<br />\n5. 國君之患：閉門自大  標榜先進  坐以待斃（一人專政萬歲）<br />\n6. 團隊之患：用人不當  小人當道  離心離德（7778婆）<br />\n7. 政權之患：民無食用  國無賢能  賞罰失威（何妖要加人工打賞8婆777）<br />\n<br />\n尚有很多例子不能盡錄<br />\n<br />\n黎明前既黑暗係至撚黑暗，重光之日就在眼前，香港人頂住！為香港而戰！"},{"pid":"408b30fdd943bd7149be4a1520b44b8dadc7574e","tid":1158180,"uid":167330,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T19:39:34.000Z","msg":"港豬仲返大陸飲緊喜茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d5c70b042571b9ab9d99d721149c97d12f0176","tid":1158180,"uid":252659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"408b30fdd943bd7149be4a1520b44b8dadc7574e","tid":1158180,"uid":167330,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T19:39:34.000Z","msg":"港豬仲返大陸飲緊喜茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T00:53:19.000Z","msg":"好事黎既<br />\n塑化劑食大d個胸"},{"pid":"313f8dbf1fd9c4c5ae5d41073e0e7b95a7056908","tid":1158180,"uid":247184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T01:20:37.000Z","msg":"最斃係而家先係岩岩日落，到黎明前香港人應該死晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c40eee0f80ab0164feb7e4c8db080d27c71f48","tid":1158180,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T00:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a